Class DesktopContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • DesktopContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AppletContext, Runnable

    public class DesktopContext
extends Object
implements AppletContext, Runnable
    An implementation of AppletContext, optimized for desktop apps. It's not complete though, only the methods needed by Nfm2 are implemented.
    Author:
    DragShot
